data.description: Attention Buyer!!! New list price. Embrace the character and craftsmanship of a bygone era with this well-maintained home, showcasing the timeless architecture and design of the 1950s. The property also offers FEMA shutters value at 10,000. Experience the comfort of three spacious bedrooms, each offering a unique retreat for relaxation and personalization.Take advantage of the spacious yard for outdoor living, gardening, or creating your own private oasis. The corner lot provides flexibility for various landscaping possibilities.Vintage touches add character to every corner of the home This property stands out on a coveted corner lot, providing extra space, privacy, and a charming street presence. The manicured yard offers the perfect backdrop for outdoor activities and gatherings. Admire the classic architecture, from the front porch to the elegant roofline. The timeless appeal of this home makes it a standout in the neighborhood.If you appreciate the allure of vintage homes and desire a property with character and history, this 1956 gem is a must-see. Schedule a showing to explore the unique charm and potential this Winter Haven residence has to offer. Seller has a 4.0 inspection report.
